      <description>&lt;p&gt;求解如下常微分方程：&lt;br&gt;
$$
\begin{aligned}
\begin{cases}
\frac{du}{dt}=-\frac{u}{t},1\leq t\leq 2, \\
u(1)=1
\end{cases}
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;</description>
